{"tid":1321451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀遊覽簡介","createTime":"2019-07-15T16:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T18:35:17.000Z","uid":34478,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6b01754f63b5916c09553a08e9b1fb5689e333a","tid":1321451,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀作為九龍半島嘅核心地區之一<br />\n香港人應該要有更多嘅認識<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sAoq46X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsAoq46X.png&h=01ac6f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n1. 地理及交通<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀喺九龍半島嘅最南面<br />\n能夠出入嘅大路只有三條：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自由行集中地 廣東道</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">九龍半島中軸線 彌敦道</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">博物館集中地 梳士巴利道+漆咸道南</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3q83fw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3q83fw.png&h=8da66aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鐵路方面 有尖沙咀站同尖東站<br />\n腳力好少少嘅可以上返附近佐敦站或者柯士甸站<br />\n甚至 你可以經尖東行紅磡站/隧道口<br />\n<br />\n有大量九巴由天星碼頭一帶出發去九龍半島唔同地方<br />\n而且大部分都途經上面三條大路<br />\n同上 如果你去到隧道口就更加多巴士通去全港九新界<br />\n<br />\n海路 有天星碼頭分別去中環同灣仔<br />\n去到紅磡碼頭又可以搭去北角 去新光睇大戲<br />\n(但係要留意 紅磡尾班船係8點前)<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n2. 附近設施<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀最多係乜嘢? 遊客同商場<br />\n而且唔止廣東道<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em>係三條大路都有</em></span><br />\n<br />\n沿路啲商場多都我都數唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">廣東道有 海港城+新港中心+力寶太陽</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">彌敦道有 iSquare 美麗華 SOGO TheOne</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">漆咸道有 新文華 東海 港晶</span><br />\n<br />\n同時又要睇埋有咩警署喎<br />\n萬一有咩事可以搵人求助呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眾所周知就聖安德烈堂對面 清真寺隔籬嘅 尖沙咀警署<br />\n<br />\n再宏觀啲呢?<br />\n有太子站旁邊嘅 旺角警署<br />\n有西九海皮嘅 新油麻地警署<br />\n有九龍城法院附近嘅 九龍城警署(<span style=\"color: blue;\">兼CCTVB最愛嘅 西九龍總區總部</span>)<br />\n有愛民邨對開嘅 紅磡警署(兼 九龍城警區總部)<br />\n所以 大家可以放心 support可以極速到達現場協助你<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n3. 路線<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀其實有條隧道打通尖沙咀站同尖東站<br />\n唔使下下出返彌敦道搵車搭<br />\n東至尖東海傍 西至力寶太陽<br />\n而力寶太陽就喺新港中心旁邊<br />\n新港中心有橋直入海港城 你話幾方便<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjjxLpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjjxLpP.png&h=4e34f15a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自認身體好 想再行多幾步?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em>無問題！</em></span><br />\n星光大道一路連住尖東海傍 再上橋<br />\n就可以去到紅磡碼頭巴士站同黃埔花園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tha83bz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftha83bz.png&h=628f1ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n忽然落雨點樣算？<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">濕撚晒唔撚驚！</span></del><br />\n只要到咗尖東海傍 去到新文華有電梯上橋連接紅磡站同理工大學<br />\n再可以延伸入去黃埔花園<br />\n有瓦遮頭仲驚佢落狗屎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYapBwD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYapBwD.png&h=a1a363b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想行公園都行架<br />\n咁大個九龍公園直通佐敦<br />\n行嗰陣仲可以睇埋鳥語花香 幾好吖<br />\n<br />\n想行下特色嘢又可以啫<br />\n金馬倫道 加拿芬道一帶有好多細舖仔<br />\n食肆又多 咩菜式都有<br />\n酒吧又多 夜晚同三五知己飲返杯 咪話唔爽"},{"pid":"0c2fa768f79910db3ab7dee2f89f558f3ca89fc7","tid":1321451,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"輕力一推"},{"pid":"b79bc60c5b29f2e7e3899f34ed7f57870edeeb3b","tid":1321451,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf3c1285d92e89cdb8db6013bcd75f64301a7ba7","tid":1321451,"uid":4015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"好詳細 推"},{"pid":"ce0f1545ecfda1444e06fde3061301163529d57c","tid":1321451,"uid":260654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"推 尖沙咀真係好好行"},{"pid":"3865ac130fc28b1197e780743a98c734bf443579","tid":1321451,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2a50e2afff41723cd8ee3f3bfc972b0de5edf06","tid":1321451,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1962d2a3fa7c3a6ea1df1123c690728d97e3d1da","tid":1321451,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b566d01873eb9d39f5db5b844656d56a07a0c26f","tid":1321451,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4d8a808440cf933a264f7aa4a8833fcf48a89f","tid":1321451,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"多謝推介!"}]}